      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car and it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super dependable for me\u2014perfect for someone who needs a reliable daily driver that still looks great in the driveway! It has some very minor signs of love from the road, but it runs beautifully and is ready for its next adventure. I'd love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see for yourself how smooth it handles!",
