    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically sound 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six engine with individual throttle bodies. This driver-spec example is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Recent preventative maintenance includes a comprehensive VANOS system refresh and a precise valve clearance adjustment to ensure optimal valvetrain harmonics. The chassis remains taut, and the rear subframe has been inspected and reinforced for long-term structural integrity. While the exterior shows minor road-derived patina, the drivetrain delivers the raw, high-revving performance characteristic of this M-division legend. A robust, sorted example ready for the apex.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
