    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a prime example of a well-maintained daily driver that balances performance with practicality. The exterior retains a beautiful gloss, with only minor stone chips and light swirl marks visible under direct sunlight, typical of a car that has been loved but driven. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary; the premium surfaces are intact, the bolsters show only light entry wear, and it has never been smoked in. Every electronic component, from the intuitive infotainment system to the crisp climate control, functions exactly as intended. Under the hood, the engine is clean and runs quietly, benefiting from a documented history of synthetic oil changes and recent fluid flushes. The transmission is seamless, providing confident power delivery whether in city traffic or on the highway. With deep tread on the tires and firm, responsive braking, this car requires no immediate investment and is ready for the long road ahead.",
